{"type":"message","id":"1f810376","parentId":"0da16ac2","timestamp":"2026-05-20T03:09:02.083Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The push_results.json has data from 2026-05-09. The current date is 2026-05-20. So this is old data. But there are only 4 jpg files (push_1.jpg to push_4.jpg), and push_5.jpg is missing.\n\nAlso, the data seems stale. We should try to get fresh data if possible. But since the MCP isn't running and Docker isn't available, we can't get fresh data.\n\nGiven the situation, I think the best approach is to use the existing data and push what we have to Feishu, noting the date discrepancy. But wait - the cron says it should run now (2026-05-20). The push_results.json is from 2026-05-09. \n\nThis is clearly outdated content. The cron was supposed to run at 11:00 AM on May 20th, 2026, but what's in the file is from 11 days prior. Without access to the MCP service, I can't fetch current data. I should inform the user about this staleness issue and ask whether they want to proceed with the old data anyway or handle this differently."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n**❌ 小红书 MCP 服务连接失败**\n\n**问题排查：**\n1. **Docker Desktop 未运行** — `com.docker.service` 处于停止状态，且当前 exec 不具备 elevated 权限启动服务\n2. **MediaCrawler MCP 端口 18080 未监听** — 尝试本地启动 `.venv` 环境但报错（缺少停用词文件 `./docs/hit_stopwords.txt`）\n\n**现有数据状态：**\n- `push_results.json` 内容日期为 **2026-05-09**，距今已 **11 天**（过期）\n- 本地封面图：`push_1.jpg` ~ `push_4.jpg`（缺少 `push_5.jpg`）\n\n---\n\n**建议解决方案（二选一）：**\n\n**方案 A — 手动启动 Docker Desktop**\n请你手动启动 Docker Desktop，等待服务就绪后我再重新执行\n\n**方案 B — 跳过 MCP，直接用现有内容推送**\n用 `push_results.json` 里 2026-05-09 的旧数据（4张图）直接推送到飞书\n\n---\n\n你希望我怎么处理？\n</final>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779246525213}}
